Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的行动全看我的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙应该没法变成龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你无法见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才不是还陪我跳舞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把戴在左手的手镯交来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能一起跳舞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能 永远不能了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等 跑太快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是红龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得死在这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是纯血龙族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说在遥远的东方边境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个与人类共存的龙族之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是个讨好人类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:01:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胆小且毫无尊严的族群
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿萨谢尔他们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来 半吊子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要淘汰你那被人类砧污的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈的血才不肮脏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔 赶紧离开那个恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人间太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦神圣之子在王都的消息走漏出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类必定会想方设法夺取你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣之子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿萨谢尔 感谢你长久以来保护着艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我得把艾尔要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜…有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有加入部队的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 剩下的交给我们处理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还只是个孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜杀她的理由何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 要是杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王可不会坐视不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的国王兴趣挺奇特的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似特别喜欢那个小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对国王来说 她这样的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无异于玩完就扔的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都陪我跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还吻过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你死之前 我就告诉你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙族姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令我杀了你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然肋骨断了 不过还能坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是变生疏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 站得起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了硬上还能咋办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说为啥贞德会来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着像是神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想尽早离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会输给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向卑微的人类出卖灵魂的魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得像你一个人解决了他似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不杀掉他们真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又冒出天真的念头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 目前最重要的是先回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跟身为神的你谈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长话短说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要妨碍陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢说你们的所作所为是正义的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了明确这点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须阻止陛下的破坏行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充其量只是反贼的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跟国王打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 凯撒 赶紧过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们什么都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒 喂 真的不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在里面不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失落成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是因为行动失败和受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王不死手镯就取不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我就打算干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果那家伙跑来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜跟国王之间发生什么事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德在这我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位天使又是从哪带来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里 一是为了将艾尔带回天界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二是为了收拾叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你点事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯王在之前的战争中使用的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说 那种魔法技术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在于很遥远的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即神和恶魔出现在这片大陆之前的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自太古时代起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等神明便封印了那种魔法技术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个破坏兵器就是用这技术制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百列大人是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪破坏力这么惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是曾经统治这片大陆的前人们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的负面遗产之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等神明都无法弄清那东西的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能封印起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯王不停袭击神界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了弄到它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何陛下能驾驭那种技术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这一点 我们也无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想问的就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该跟我回神殿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔 你不愿待在我身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量是为了履行责任而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 为了让世界恢复和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在必须战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是为此而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为此而生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生的理由只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老爸是为了你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才把你赐给她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这话有根据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要带我来人间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我回神界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在那瞎编
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日后出啥麻烦我可不管哦
