Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 姆伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回神界了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
