Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就跟姆伽罗一起在马车睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经成长了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 走吧 姆伽罗真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢 你去干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去艾博斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到时候了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要解除狭缝的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚 我把红龙处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚的入侵者 貌似到头来没抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会还在王宫里吧
