Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没看见 没在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法陪你们一起战斗 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 凯撒队长
