Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我似乎多少能理解一点你的感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
